OL,3,CPolice push for phone companies to be
OL,4,Cforced to make stolen handsets unusable
OL,6,FBritain's biggest police force is
OL,7,Fpushing the Home Secretary to force
OL,8,Fphone companies to make stolen devices
OL,9,Fharder to reuse as chief Sir Mark
OL,10,FRowley continues a crusade to make the
OL,11,Fhandsets "unusable bricks".
OL,13,FSir Mark issued an ultimatum in March
OL,14,Fcalling on telecoms giants to take
OL,15,Faction to make phones less desirable
OL,16,Fto steal by making them impossible to
OL,17,Freuse.
OL,26,@sD@JOUsD@ZO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/12
