PN,40702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781348571
OL,3,CPolice push for phone companies to be
OL,4,Cforced to make stolen handsets unusable
OL,6,FOn Thursday the force revealed it has
OL,7,Fstarted sharing data with Apple to
OL,8,Fmore closely track whether stolen
OL,9,Fhandsets get reconnected to a phone
OL,10,Fnetwork after they are taken.
OL,12,FSpeaking after an operation that
OL,13,Ftargeted two phone shops in north
OL,14,FLondon on Wednesday, Sir Mark said
OL,15,Fthat the information from Apple will
OL,16,Fallow officers to build up a global
OL,17,Fpicture of what happens to stolen
OL,18,Fhandsets.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781348571
OL,3,CPolice push for phone companies to be
OL,4,Cforced to make stolen handsets unusable
OL,6,FHe told said: "If we share the data we
OL,7,Fhave on the phone stolen, with the
OL,8,Fdata they have on things like
OL,9,Freactivations and future uses of
OL,10,Fphones, we can get a global picture of
OL,11,Fphones being stolen, are they being
OL,12,Freactivated, are they being broken
OL,13,Fdown for parts, where they're being
OL,14,Fexported to in the world.
OL,26,@nD@OOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781348571
OL,3,CPolice push for phone companies to be
OL,4,Cforced to make stolen handsets unusable
OL,6,F"We're already seeing, whereas a few
OL,7,Fmonths ago the majority of stolen
OL,8,Fphones were being reactivated because
OL,9,Fof security flaws, now with the
OL,10,Fsecurity improvements it's the
OL,11,Fminority being reactivated, that means
OL,12,Fit's harder for criminals to profit,
OL,13,Fthat will help bring down the crime
OL,14,Ffurther."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@IO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/12
