OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1781348571
OL,3,CPolice push for phone companies to be
OL,4,Cforced to make stolen handsets unusable
OL,6,FThe international trade in stolen
OL,7,Fphones is worth millions of dollars,
OL,8,Fwith a device stolen in London worth
OL,9,Fmore in countries like China because
OL,10,Fit has none of the government
OL,11,Frestrictions put in place by
OL,12,Fauthorities there.
OL,14,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/12
